🔐 Password Generator – Secure, Flexible, and Customizable**
This project is a terminal-based password generator written in Python.
It allows users to generate secure passwords with custom length and character types.
Users can choose to include uppercase, lowercase, digits, and special characters.
There is also an option to generate 5 strong suggestions to choose from.
The script uses `colorama` to add visual clarity with colored terminal output.
It's beginner-friendly, well-commented, and easy to customize for any purpose.
Ideal for developers, sysadmins, and anyone needing secure password generation.
Can be extended to include clipboard copy, file saving, or GUI interface.
